OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly cloudy day with some
OL,6,Fbright or sunny intervals breaking
OL,7,Fthrough. Largely dry but a few light
OL,8,Foutbreaks of rain possible through the
OL,9,Fday. Moderate to fresh southerly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FCloud will break up this
OL,12,Fevening and the rest of the night will
OL,13,Fbe dry with some clear spells.
OL,14,FModerate to fresh southerly winds.
OL,15,
OL,16,CTuesday:FA dry bright start then
OL,17,Fclouding over with a little patchy
OL,18,Frain. Brightening up again later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
