OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FWednesday will be a showery day with
OL,7,Fstrong to gale force winds. Thursday
OL,8,Fcloudy with rain, heavy at times,
OL,9,Fbrighter later. Friday brighter with a
OL,10,Ffew showers, less windy.
